    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Workspace API Examples\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"This notebook demonstrates how to work with Evo Workspaces using **direct API calls**, providing granular control over workspace operations and detailed insight into the underlying service interactions.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"### API vs SDK Approach\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"This notebook uses **direct Workspace API calls** which:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- ✅ Provides full control over API requests and responses\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- ✅ Shows detailed API response structures and metadata\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- ✅ Allows for advanced customization and fine-tuning\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- ✅ Helps understand the underlying service architecture\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- ✅ Useful for debugging and advanced use cases\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"### Want a Simpler, High-Level Interface?\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"If you prefer a more streamlined experience with less boilerplate code, check out the `sdk-examples.ipynb` notebook in this same directory. The SDK examples show:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Simplified method calls using `WorkspaceAPIClient`\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Automatic handling of complex API interactions\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Better error handling and validation\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Recommended for most common use cases\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"1\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
